ddf.mime.custom

Class CustomMimeTypeResolver

  • java.lang.Object
    • ddf.mime.custom.CustomMimeTypeResolver
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    MimeTypeResolver

    public class CustomMimeTypeResolver
extends Object
implements MimeTypeResolver
    DDF custom mime type resolution packaged as a MimeTypeResolver OSGi service that can map a list of custom file extensions to their corresponding custom mime types, and vice versa. Currently used to add image/nitf mime type support.
    Since:
    2.1.0

        public String getFileExtensionForMimeType(String mimeType)
        Description copied from interface: MimeTypeResolver
        Gets the file extension for the specific mime type. For example, if the mime type is image/nitf a file extension of .nitf would be returned. The mapping of file extensions to mime types is part of the configuration of a MimeTypeResolver.
